source:
TEXT_BANQIQ124_03829_SEQ_00Qhoterl Pasol has the look of someone who hasn't had all she can eat.

※Please note that the difficulty of this quest has been synced to your current level. Furthermore, you may not proceed with a class or job that is different from when you accepted this quest.
target:
TEXT_BANQIQ124_03829_SEQ_00Règle spéciale:  synchronisation de quête avec limitation de job ou de classe
* Il n'est possible de progresser dans cette quête qu'avec la classe qui a servi à la commencer.

Qhoterl Pasol est excitée comme une puce.

source: TEXT_BANQIQ124_03829_TODO_00<tab>Speak with the poultryman at Slitherbough.
target: TEXT_BANQIQ124_03829_TODO_00<tab>Parler à l'éleveur de poules, à Serpentige

source: TEXT_BANQIQ124_03829_TODO_01<tab>Use the large sack to capture the clucking chicken.
target: TEXT_BANQIQ124_03829_TODO_01<tab>Attraper la poule fugueuse à l'aide <var 33 ((EventItem)) 0AF61E90240202 /var>

source: TEXT_BANQIQ124_03829_TODO_02<tab>Deliver the clucking sack to the poultryman.
TEXT_BANQIQ124_03829_TODO_03<tab>Deliver the splendid eggs to Qhoterl Pasol.

TEXT_BANQIQ124_03829_QHOTERLPASOL_000_000<tab>The other day residents from Slitherbough brought a gift most divine─chicken eggs! And let me tell you, to say that their flavor was transcendent hardly begins to describe the experience!
target: TEXT_BANQIQ124_03829_QHOTERLPASOL_000_000<tab>Peuple de Nuit être amis amis avec Qitari<var 1D /var>! Offrir souvent œufs frais<var 1D /var>! Qitari ne pas savoir à quel point œufs être bons avant de rencontrer peuple de Nuit<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_BANQIQ124_03829_QHOTERLPASOL_000_001<tab>I had scarce tasted the first egg when I knew we must have more. Being the enterprising Qitari that I am, I've arranged to exchange our precious stones for their precious eggs. One of nature's bounties for another─a capital bargain if I do say so myself!
target: TEXT_BANQIQ124_03829_QHOTERLPASOL_000_001<tab>Œuf être aliment très nuuutritif, et explorateurs toujours avoir besoin d'être au top de forme, alors Qhoterl Pasol souvent échanger œufs contre cristaux pouvant servir de pierres baptismales à peuple de Nuit.

source: TEXT_BANQIQ124_03829_QHOTERLPASOL_000_002<tab>We have already delivered our first cache of stones, but someone must pick up the eggs from Slitherbough. If you would be so kind, I'll ensure that you're handsomely compensated!
target: TEXT_BANQIQ124_03829_QHOTERLPASOL_000_002<tab>Et Qhoterl Pasol justement venir de recevoir message disant que œufs être prêts<var 1D /var>! <var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 02 /var> bien vouloir aller en chercher un et rapporter<var 1D /var>! Obtenir grosse récompense si gentil<var 08 E905 ((le)) (()) /var> gentil<var 08 E905 ((le)) (()) /var><var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_BANQIQ124_03829_POULTRYFARMER03829_000_010<tab>I take it you're here about the eggs, then? I'd love to give them to you, but I'm afraid I've run into a snag. One of my chickens fled the coop, you see, clucking like the sky itself was falling down!
target: TEXT_BANQIQ124_03829_POULTRYFARMER03829_000_010<tab>Ah, c'est pour l'œuf des Qitari<var 1D /var>? Je suis désolé, mais je ne peux pas vous le donner maintenant<var 1D /var>! Ma poule pondeuse la plus prolifique s'est échappée du poulailler et il faut absolument que je la retrouve<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_BANQIQ124_03829_POULTRYFARMER03829_000_011<tab>Gods only know where she is now, but I reckon I'd find her quicker if I had another set of eyes looking for her. What say you? Lend a hand and I'll give you the pick of my best eggs!
target: TEXT_BANQIQ124_03829_POULTRYFARMER03829_000_011<tab>Elle a toujours été peureuse, alors elle ne peut pas être allée bien loin. Dites, vous voulez bien la chercher avec moi<var 1D /var>? Si vous acceptez, je vous promets de vous donner le plus gros œuf de sa ponte pour vous remercier<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_BANQIQ124_03829_POULTRYFARMER03829_000_012<tab>If you catch sight of her, use this sack to scoop her up. I'll stay around the village, while you go ahead and look around the outskirts─I reckon you might hear her before you see her!
target: TEXT_BANQIQ124_03829_POULTRYFARMER03829_000_012<tab>Tenez, prenez <var 33 ((EventItem)) 07F61E90240202 /var> et mettez-la dedans, elle croira que la nuit est tombée et s'endormira im<var 16 /var>mé<var 16 /var>dia<var 16 /var>te<var 16 /var>ment. Essayez de la retrouver dans l'enceinte du village pendant que je jette un œil dans la forêt, d'accord<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_BANQIQ124_03829_POULTRYFARMER03829_000_020<tab>I've searched everywhere, but I haven't seen hide nor down of that pesky bird. I hope you've had better luck than me.
target: TEXT_BANQIQ124_03829_POULTRYFARMER03829_000_020<tab>J'ai eu beau fouiner partout, je n'ai pas entendu le moindre caquètement... Et vous<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_BANQIQ124_03829_POULTRYFARMER03829_000_021<tab>Ah, that's her all right! You're a godssend! I was worried she'd been gobbled up whole by some bigger animal. She always lays the best eggs─it would've been a tragedy to lose her.
target: TEXT_BANQIQ124_03829_POULTRYFARMER03829_000_021<tab>Oh, merci beaucoup, m<var 08 E905 ((a sauveuse)) ((on sauveur)) /var><var 1D /var>! J'ai bien cru que ma plus grosse source de revenus avait fini dans le ventre d'un monstre... Sans parler de ses œufs qui nourrissent tout le monde ici<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_BANQIQ124_03829_POULTRYFARMER03829_000_022<tab>Speaking of eggs, I believe these are for you. And as I promised, here's a few more on top as your just reward. Give my regards to the Qitari, and let them know I'm open for business any time!
target: TEXT_BANQIQ124_03829_POULTRYFARMER03829_000_022<tab>Voici le plus gros œuf de la ponte pour les Qitari. Passez le bonjour à tout le monde de ma part, et merci encore<var 1D /var>!

source:
TEXT_BANQIQ124_03829_QHOTERLPASOL_000_030Would that the Qitari could lay eggs. Hmm, perhaps if I...
Oh! You're back! Do you have them!? Do you!?

TEXT_BANQIQ124_03829_QHOTERLPASOL_000_031Oh, you have saved─
Hmph, I mean, splendid! These eggs are even more pleasing to behold than the last batch, and there are so many of them! I would've sent one of my workers to fetch these, but the sad truth is that no Qitari could be trusted with the task.
target: TEXT_BANQIQ124_03829_QHOTERLPASOL_000_031<tab>Oooh<var 1D /var>! Être encore plus gros que d'habituuude<var 1D /var>! Qitari être content content<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_BANQIQ124_03829_QHOTERLPASOL_000_032<tab>The eggs would have been devoured before they were one yalm from Slitherbough. That you showed enough restraint to deliver them untouched truly speaks to your heroic pedigree!
target: TEXT_BANQIQ124_03829_QHOTERLPASOL_000_032<tab>D'habitude, Qhoterl Pasol envoyer autre Qitari amateur d'œufs pour aider à maigrir avant de s'empiffrer<var 1D /var>! Mais <var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 02 /var> pas besoin de faire régime, être svelte comme Qhoterl Pasol<var 1D /var>!
